Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent Luffy and\NNami from reaching the ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru released Mamaragan. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land won't be beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was approaching the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over... the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:19.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear with the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fi... re... works!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Peony!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Ring the "fire of Shandora"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally reached the ark, and at\Nthe end of the fierce fight with Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll ring you as well!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gold Rifle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle Ends! Proud Fantasia Echoes Far"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?!\NOld diamond-head! Monkeys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold... was right here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bonehead did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty sound! What is this?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that this moment\Nwould come one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was the ring that Noland heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suu... I wonder if Vearth is singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So God really... exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had half given up on the bell ringing\Nagain after its 400-year silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Warrior Calgara... Can you hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the echo of the fire of Shandora...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to this land?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this tone? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the legendary...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hearing this... Montblanc Noland?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this reaches your descendants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like this bell's sound, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer! Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one bell in\Nthis world that echoes this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--From the sky...\N--I'm getting worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the monsters that appear\Nwith the cumuloregalis clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there used to be a story like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a human far up in the sky\Nand strong sunlight shines on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his figure is reflected in\Nthe deep mist of the far sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow looks as if it's a huge monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the true form of those monsters are\Nthe shadows of the humans in the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean that we've already\Nconfirmed that people live in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the story was a meaningless\Nfantasy and I'd forgotten about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems that it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the loud ring of the golden bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold really exists in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:05.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noland The Liar"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noland wasn't... My ancestor wasn't a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rang it to tell me that from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right, kid? I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monkey"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Old-timer?!\N--What's the matter?! Are you sick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids... I'm glad they were safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru and his ship are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell's ring is the fire of Shandora,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a long-gone city that\Ntook pride in its prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island's singing voice that\Nproclaims the end of the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promised ring was\Ndelivered after 400 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the journey of\Nthe restless island was long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to forget the distant memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, people entrusted their\Nwords in the sound of the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They placed proud words in\Nthe song sent to the distant sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... if the old guy\Nand the others heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're... right here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie the ropes to strong-looking trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa... Were you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here... your treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How's everyone else?\N--They're fine! Don't speak right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You have to get treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treatment can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before treating me, do something\Nabout that guy, or he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! His body's falling apart,\Nright down to the bones. This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's one of the guerrillas.\NWe don't owe him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't really know why, but it\Nseemed like he was going all out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck?\NAre you feeling sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna be okay, Raccoon-Doggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer! Look, I have antlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, go and rest with those Blue Sea people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, hurry up and go bring the families!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the end, both the golden\Nbell and Eneru's golden ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now it's a city of gold in name only, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means our journey\Nin poverty continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want those dials rather than gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we won't be able to get them\Nonce we get back to the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I wonder if Nami-san's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Conis-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to leave Wyper\Nwith the Blue Sea people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It seems that\NAisa made friends with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we have to hurry.\NIt's pointless if our enemy wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather those who can move.\NWe'll banish the priests to the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All he needs now is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!! Conis-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I'm glad you are okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried, but I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan, so you were\Nworried about me that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that food, you guys? Where'd you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found the priests' food storage\Non our way back through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you get down from that height?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used my Gum-Gum Balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Conis, where's your old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... um... he protected me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're talking about you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the White Sea on the lower level?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I found myself there\Nafter being knocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who came down to the lower\Nlevel heading towards Cloud End
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are also coming back to the White-White Sea\Nvia restored Milky Roads right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, since there's\Nno Angel Island anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're heading towards Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you very much.\N--Thank you very much, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer known by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all forced to work in a place\Nlike this for six long years. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Angel Island, the home\Nwe were supposed to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shandians, too, lost their home,\NVillage Hidden in the Clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the battle really over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's army is gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, is the 400-year rift\Nsomething that can be filled so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boy, I stuffed myself!\N--It's totally night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go back to the ship now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! If we go back to the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can have a long relaxed\Nsleep in a warm bed, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Usopp, you heard what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's terrible. Not thinking\Nanything after seeing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're unqualified to be\Na pirate-- no, to be a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That"? What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning... to where God should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that obstruct my field\Nof vision cannot exist in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all were in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have it. It's fit just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boundless land, just like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's set off, Maxim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To God's world that\Nfloats brightly in the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the land without end, the Endless Vearth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the ruins of Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shouldn't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... are a Skypiean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Were we captured by the Skypieans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no distinction among\Nthose injured in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden belfry... We still have\Nthe duty to protect it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sound of drums announcing a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's fire on the ruins, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Wyper. Wait a little\Nand see how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of heroic reason for\Nthe fight there was in the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to us who live in the present time,\Nthis sky is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land, at least, is not refusing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this very moment, there's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Go ahead and\Ncheck it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, no one wants to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold our true motive in your\Nhearts and speak not of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn those words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the words engraved on the belfry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient weapon Poseidon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Gold Roger...?\NCould the Rio Poneglyph be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates, you know.\NNow, let's snatch the gold and run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Made It Here! The Yarn the Poneglyphs Spin"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
